snippet.title: 7 Really Strange Birth-Related Stories

localized.description:
A short video I created about some really strange and bizarre birth stories from around the world, like twins with different fathers, different Colored Twins, Oldest Mother, youngest mother, and others. Quintuplets.

Music:
Finding the Balance - Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
